headline.main: China Trims 2017 Growth Target, Warns Against Trade Controls
headline.print_headline: China Trims 2017 Growth Target, Warns Against Trade Controls

lead_paragraph: China's top economic official trimmed its growth target and warned Sunday of dangers from global pressure for trade controls, as Beijing tries to build a consumer-driven economy and reduce reliance on exports and investment.
